{"tid":824821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布明天繼續停課","createTime":"2018-09-17T08:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T13:21:19.000Z","uid":79382,"like":42,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"824feade2a155a8963aa99e0075dd4bf155b139c","tid":824821,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"教育局宣布明天繼續停課教育局宣布明天繼續停課<br />\n<br />\n超強颱風「山竹」災情未解決，教育局下午宣布，所有學校明日繼續停課。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537170385794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537170385794&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1abf568c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180917%2Fs00001%2F1537170385794&h=fc33f10b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180917/s00001/1537170385794</a>"},{"pid":"39e67155cfe6f17cf8e03cc93ca1a333dd3b3578","tid":824821,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:49:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849f08004c8614613790d9f02c6eedac4dc07666","tid":824821,"uid":190943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:50:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38b90f36921f7cef6e17b88b84a4f89c516d69b6","tid":824821,"uid":79382,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:51:00.000Z","msg":"但係大學聽日就開始要上堂<br />\n又多一批人同大家迫<br />\n<br />\n利申 火車撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8e63c3ff0b4654681c4ec837b213116ac6a953","tid":824821,"uid":206080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:51:47.000Z","msg":"HKU冇得停<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9860362201a9716b153a9df61dbc101810bc33","tid":824821,"uid":124473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:51:53.000Z","msg":"超強颱風「山竹」災情未解決??<br />\n<br />\n學生: 未解決<br />\n工人: 已解決"},{"pid":"9a774e97dc1a57c49c048341ace599706a5365d6","tid":824821,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠宣布明天繼續返工"},{"pid":"e54b6f4e284edc630d22af608c6a40a887156ad2","tid":824821,"uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/165308_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F165308_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=da9b42f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23bce56ff8c183a7324ab4073795b7e37b50af78","tid":824821,"uid":15693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"教育局宣布明日所有學校繼續停課<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　由於強颱風山竹對學校造成不同程度影響，部分學校需時清理及維修校舍和設施，加上公共交通服務尚待完全恢復正常，為確保學生的安全，教育局宣布明日（九月十八日）所有學校停課。<br />\n<br />\n　　在安全的情況下，學校應保持校舍開放，並實施校本應急計劃，安排人手在校內安全的地方照顧有確切需要回校的學生。家長應考慮家居環境、附近的道路交通情況、學生的照顧等因素決定是否送子女回校。<br />\n<br />\n  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2018年9月17日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間16時45分<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201809/17/P2018091701226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201809%2F17%2FP2018091701226.htm&d=zY%2FQSSMQZOo%2Fp9VqewScKsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d07eff92\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201809/17/P2018091701226.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d0d3d83bfe9b52c08e4f2d6f72ca6088447321b9","tid":824821,"uid":54754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"做中小學堆教畜真係爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9959b8ec54e9fbf5af5aaec776ed21112c0d9fbe","tid":824821,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc